<section class="content-section reveal">
  <h2>How to Use This Calculator</h2>

  <p>Enter your <strong>loan amount</strong> and <strong>interest rate</strong>. The calculator instantly shows your payment amount, total interest, total cost, and payoff date.</p>

  <p>Need to adjust the term or payment schedule? Expand <strong>"More options"</strong> to change the <strong>loan term</strong> (1–30 years) or switch between <strong>monthly</strong> and <strong>biweekly</strong> payments. Biweekly payments result in 26 payments per year instead of 12 — you'll pay off the loan faster and save on interest.</p>

